Они часто используются для создания разделительных полос или полос слияния во время строительства дорог или автомобильных аварий.

ORIGINAL: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
ENGLISH: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
CZECH: Ikarus 260 je meziměstský a linkový autobus vyráběný maďarským výrobcem Ikarus od roku 1971 do roku 2002. Odolnost a spolehlivost tohoto modelu významně vysvětlují jeho nevídanou dlouhověkost. Na druhé straně je třeba zdůraznit, že tento model měl být nahrazen koncem 80. let, ale výrobce, který měl finanční potíže kvůli pozdním platbám od veřejných zákazníků v zemích RVHP, nemohl financovat nový vývoj. Objednávky bývalého SSSR a Německa v roce 1990 prudce klesly, což přivedlo Ikarus na pokraj bankrotu. Ikarus zahájil sérii 400, ale zákazníci požadovali spolehlivější sérii 200.
GERMAN: Der Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
RUSSIAN: Икарус 260 - это междугородний и линейный автобус, выпускаемый венгерским производителем Икарус с 1971 по 2002 год. Прочность и надежность этой модели во многом объясняют ее беспрецедентную долговечность. С другой стороны, следует подчеркнуть, что эту модель следовало заменить в конце 1980-х годов, но производитель, столкнувшись с финансовыми трудностями из-за просроченных платежей от государственных заказчиков в странах СЭВ, не мог финансировать новые разработки. Заказы из бывшего СССР и Германии рухнули в 1990 году, поставив «Икарус» на грань банкротства. Икарус запустил серию 400, но покупатели требовали более надежную серию 200.
POLISH: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
HUNGARIAN: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
ITALIAN: L'Ikarus 260 è un Autobus Intercity e di Linea prodotto dalla Ungherese Ikarus tra il 1971 ed il 2002. La robustezza e l'affidabilità di questo modello spiegano la sua impareggiata longevità. Dall'altro lato, dovrebbe essere noto che questo modello avrebbe dovuto essere rimpiazzato negli anni 80 ma il produttore, in difficoltà finanziarie per via di pagamenti tardivi da parte di clienti pubblici negli stati del Comecon, non poté finanziare nuovi modelli. Gli ordini dalla ex USSR e Germania cessarono nel 1990, mettendo Ikarus sull'orlo della bancarotta. Ikarus lanciò poi la serie 400 ma i clienti richiesro comunque la più affidabile serie 200.
SPANISH: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
FRENCH: L‘Ikarus 260 est un autobus interurbain et de ligne fabriqué par le constructeur hongrois Ikarus de 1971 à 2002. La robustesse et la fiabilité de ce modèle expliquent en grande partie sa longévité sans équivalent. Il faut par contre souligner que ce modèle aurait dû être remplacé dès la fin des années 1980 mais le constructeur, en difficulté financières dues aux retards de paiement des clients publics des États du Comecon ne put financer de nouveaux développements. Les commandes de l'ex URSS et de l'Allemagne s'effondrèrent dès 1990 mettant Ikarus au bord de la faillite. Ikarus a lancé la série 400 mais les clients réclamaient la série 200 plus fiable.
CHINESE: Ikarus 260是匈牙利製造商Ikarus於1971年至2002年生產的城際和線路巴士。 該型號的堅固性和可靠性在很大程度上解釋了它的無與倫比的長壽。 另一方面，應該強調的是，該型號應該在1980年代末被替換，但由於來自COMECON國家的公共客戶的付款延遲而導致的財務困難，製造商無法為新的研發提供資金支持。 1990年，來自前蘇聯和德國的訂單急劇下降，使Ikarus瀕臨破產邊緣。 Ikarus推出了400系列，但客戶要求更可靠的200系列。
PORTUGUESE: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
JAPANESE: The Ikarus 260 is an intercity and line bus manufactured by the Hungarian manufacturer Ikarus from 1971 to 2002. The robustness and reliability of this model largely explain its unparalleled longevity. On the other hand, it should be emphasized that this model should have been replaced at the end of the 1980s but the manufacturer, in financial difficulty due to late payments from public customers in the Comecon States, could not finance new developments. Orders from the former USSR and Germany collapsed in 1990, putting Ikarus on the verge of bankruptcy. Ikarus launched the 400 series but customers demanded the more reliable 200 series.
CHINESESIMP: Ikarus 260是1971年至2002年由匈牙利制造商Ikarus制造的城际和线路巴士。该模型的坚固性和可靠性在很大程度上说明了其无与伦比的使用寿命。另一方面，应该强调的是，该模型应该在1980年代末被替换，但是制造商由于来自Comecon州公共客户的滞纳金而陷入财务困境，无法为新的发展提供资金。 1990年，前苏联和德国的订单崩溃，使伊卡洛斯（Ikarus）濒临破产。 Ikarus推出了400系列，但客户要求更可靠的200系列。

ORIGINAL: The Vodnik is a Russian high-mobility multipurpose military vehicle manufactured by GAZ. It is a "heavy modification" of the civil GAZ-2330 "Tigr". Its name comes from the Russian "водник" – a person employed in water transport, but is also used to refer to some person or object simply related to water. A better translation would be water bearer as in the astrological sign Aquarius.
ENGLISH: The Vodnik is a Russian high-mobility multipurpose military vehicle manufactured by GAZ. It is a "heavy modification" of the civil GAZ-2330 "Tigr". Its name comes from the Russian "водник" – a person employed in water transport, but is also used to refer to some person or object simply related to water. A better translation would be water bearer as in the astrological sign Aquarius.
CZECH: Vodník je ruské víceúčelové vojenské vozidlo s vysokou mobilitou vyráběné společností GAZ. Jedná se o "těžkou modifikaci" civilního vozidla GAZ-2330 "Tigr". Jeho název pochází z ruského slova "водник", což znamená osoba zaměstnaná vodní dopravou, ale také se používá k označení osoby nebo objektu spojeného s vodou. Lepší překlad by byl vodonoš, jak je uvedeno ve znamení Vodnář v astrologii.
GERMAN: The Vodnik is a Russian high-mobility multipurpose military vehicle manufactured by GAZ. It is a "heavy modification" of the civil GAZ-2330 "Tigr". Its name comes from the Russian "водник" – a person employed in water transport, but is also used to refer to some person or object simply related to water. A better translation would be water bearer as in the astrological sign Aquarius.
RUSSIAN: Водник - российский высокомобильный многоцелевой военный автомобиль производства ГАЗ. Это «тяжелая модификация» гражданского ГАЗ-2330 «Тигр». Его название происходит от русского «водник» - человек, занятый на водном транспорте, но также используется для обозначения человека или объекта, просто связанного с водой. Лучшим переводом было бы водонос, как в астрологическом знаке Водолея.

Its name comes from the Russian "водник" – a person employed in water transport, but is also used to refer to some person or object simply related to water. A better translation would be water bearer as in the astrological sign Aquarius.

ITALIAN: Il Vodnik è un veicolo militare multiruolo estremamente agile prodotto da GAZ. Questa è una "Modifica Estrema" del GAZ-2330 civile "Tigr". Il suo nome, proviene dal russo "водник" - una persona impiegata nel trasporto su acqua, ma anche usato per riferirsi a persone od oggetti semplicemente legati all'acqua. Una traduzione migliore sarebbe "Portatore D'Acqua", come nella costellazione Astrologica dell' Acquario.

Son nom vient du russe "водник" - une personne employée dans le transport par eau, mais il est également utilisé pour désigner une personne ou un objet simplement lié à l'eau. Une meilleure traduction serait porteur d'eau comme dans le signe astrologique Verseau.

A better translation would be water bearer as in the astrological sign Aquarius.
